iframeHtml.description:
The iframHtml value is directly rendered in an iframe. The rendered stripe form in iframe will handle the necessary steps for completing the payment and post a message back to the parent window with payment status, this can be used for user feedback in the frontend.
    // window.addEventListener("message", function(event) { ... }
    // Following is the relevant info from the event object 
    {
      ...
      data: {
        type: "payment_success" // or "payment_error"
        message: "" // Error description if there was an error
      }
      ...
    }

Booking is successful when the payment_success message is received, until then the booking will be in incomplete status.

